{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Hybrid: Bottom Tabs + Drawer\n      Bottom tabs for the top 4 field-critical views (Map, Fleet, Bases, Alerts). A compact hamburger or \"more\" button opens a drawer for everything else (Overview, Missions, Telemetry, Audit, Settings). Best of both worlds.\n      \n        ProsFast access to what field ops need mostNothing is hidden — secondary items still reachableMatches the \"status + light ops\" priority\n        ConsMost complex to implementTwo mobile nav components to build and maintainNeeds careful item selection for bottom bar","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1774828545524}
